      <title>橡树校友从信贷压力中转向更高质量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/oaktree-alums-pivot-toward-higher-quality-from-stressed-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在过去的一年里，橡树资本集团的两位校友——当他们推出 Shorecliff 资产管理公司时，他们从压力中转向投资于更高质量的绩效信贷 –他们监管的资产总额增加了两倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/oaktree-alums-pivot-toward-higher-quality-from-stressed-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
